{"tid":1117898,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國醫院錯摘病人左眼球　法院：患者、醫院都有責任","createTime":"2019-04-21T04:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T07:31:41.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3b152a7328606f3bf50c4612ab29254076b82e40","tid":1117898,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"中國山西太原有一名男子發現，他接受視神經切除手術後，左眼球被醫院偷偷摘除，又稱「愛爾眼科醫院」隱瞞此事近8年。去年他向院方賠償誤工費、護理費等，共計159萬餘元人民幣（約730.51萬元台幣）。太原市迎澤區人民法院近日審理後，認為醫院和患者都得承擔一半的責任，院方需賠償34萬餘元人民幣（約156.21萬元台幣）。<br />\n小胡（化名）向《澎湃新聞》表示， 2010年6月，他因為左眼不適，到太原愛爾眼科醫院求診，院方對他進行左眼眶內腫物摘除術，同年7月出院。2011年4月，他又因為復發，而到山西省人民醫院，接受「左眼眶內腦膜瘤復發腫瘤切除術」。直到去年，小胡才在一次檢查中，無意間發現左眼球已被摘除，還被安裝假眼球，他和父親認為，山西省人民醫院是官方醫院，不會偷摘器官，定是愛爾眼科醫院所為，而把對方告上法院。<br />\n愛爾眼科醫院的醫務副主任崔蕾否認指控，但對於小胡的左眼何時被摘除，則不知情。住院病歷顯示，小胡的術後檢查及超聲波檢查均證明左眼球未被摘除。她說：「這些病歷資料都是沒問題的，如果患者認為有篡改，可以向相關部門提出鑑定」。 崔蕾續指，手術前已告知小胡，手術可能發生的併發症和風險，包括可能會失明，他也簽署同意書。而手術期間，「執刀醫生發現患者（小胡）的情況比較複雜，得把視神經一併切除，這就表示會左眼失明」。<br />\n人民法院的法官認為，雖然無法判定小胡的左眼球，是否為愛爾眼科醫院摘除，但患者在診療中受到損害，醫療機構及醫務人員有過錯，需向患者賠償。<br />\n對此，崔蕾稱，他們對鑑定結果（小胡在診療中受到損害）和法院判決結果有異議，正考慮上訴，且已向相關部門提出申請，要求查閱患者出院後的其他就診紀錄，希望可徹底查明到底是哪家醫院摘除小胡的左眼球。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190421/640_6e5492951dc3367de608b05b62f5d333.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190421%2F640_6e5492951dc3367de608b05b62f5d333.jpg&h=3d02bc2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190421/640_6f71404781f06f96e34f5e12ba95c027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190421%2F640_6f71404781f06f96e34f5e12ba95c027.jpg&h=5cb139ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190421/640_3f7832456408379befc5943ec3d995d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190421%2F640_3f7832456408379befc5943ec3d995d1.jpg&h=53a6062b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190421/1554096/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190421%2F1554096%2F&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAn4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=1fa52301\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190421%2F1554096%2F&h=ffcd8670\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190421/1554096/</a>"},{"pid":"9efcc355288dfda4380a0183e960706cdd642ae0","tid":1117898,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"super 啦,好公平個個都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aeec7ca9b13350167850e47548a38d3e9e9755c","tid":1117898,"uid":7369,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"民建聯建議引入大陸醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ae2fa694e71c04e7b8ed872ca6c2f7cd2f71c0","tid":1117898,"uid":64884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"可能佢隻眼係寫輪眼呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78bb927e19f95c022e8090e65c42df059233eab","tid":1117898,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9efcc355288dfda4380a0183e960706cdd642ae0","tid":1117898,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"super 啦,好公平個個都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf357616c74dd08785eebf7e9